text: Eunidia mediomaculatoides is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1981.BioLib.cz - Eunidia mediomaculatoides. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1981
